WEBVTT

00:00:01.928 --> 00:00:05.993
So ... we're in a real live war
at the moment,

00:00:06.017 --> 00:00:08.431
and it's a war that we're truly losing.

00:00:08.970 --> 00:00:10.815
It's a war on superbugs.

00:00:13.692 --> 00:00:15.523
So you might wonder,

00:00:15.547 --> 00:00:17.605
if I'm going to talk about superbugs,

00:00:17.629 --> 00:00:21.861
why I'm showing you a photograph
of some soccer fans --

00:00:21.885 --> 00:00:25.106
Liverpool soccer fans
celebrating a famous victory

00:00:25.130 --> 00:00:27.232
in Istanbul, a decade ago.

00:00:28.233 --> 00:00:30.393
In the back, in the red shirt,